      "content": "i mean i get that it's not ideal but i feel okay right now. i've had a tiny bit of wine before with meds and nothing happened. usually people say a little bit is fine as long as you eat a big meal with it to soak it up. isn't it just a precaution? like, if i just have one glass max, is it really gonna make me that sick? i really don't want to ruin the dinner.",
